pleased to invite you to a special program organized to mark the successful completion of a Leadership Expedition conducted from 17 December to 27 December 2025.

The program aims to:

hotelDescription:
In a dense neighborhood, this laid-back guesthouse with a nearby annex is 7 minutes away on foot from Boudhanath, an ancient domed stupa, 3 km from the Hindu Pashupatinath temple and 4 km from Tribhuvan International Airport.
 The conservative rooms offer Wi-Fi. Rooms in the annex add air-conditioning, and upgraded rooms offer balconies, some with views of the Boudhanath Stupa.
 There's a restaurant/bakery with seating in an enclosed garden. Parking and breakfast are available.

ownerUpdates.text:
Amazing Himalayan Views from Nepalaya Rooftop! 

Today’s view is truly special — clear and breathtaking sights of Ganesh Himal and the Langtang Himalayan range right from our rooftop. 

Enjoy delicious food, warm hospitality, and the best mountain views in the heart of Thamel. 

📍 Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant – Hotel Nepalaya, Thamel
🌐

Warm Hospitality, Delicious Food & Beautiful Views! 

At Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant, we believe every guest deserves an unforgettable dining experience — with friendly service, cozy atmosphere, and a stunning view of Kathmandu city! 

Come and enjoy your favorite meals with our smiling team and peaceful rooftop vibes in the heart of Thamel.

📍 Hotel Nepalaya Rooftop, Thamel, Kathmandu
🌐

Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant – Thamel’s Hidden Gem! 

If you are in Kathmandu, you must visit Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant at least once! 
Enjoy the amazing city and mountain views, delicious food, and the most friendly staff who make you feel right at home. 

🍛 Taste our special Nepalese Thali, Biryani, and fresh pizza.
☕ Relax with tea or coffee while watching the sunset over the rooftops of Thamel.

✨ Beautiful view, good food, and great people – everything you need for a perfect time in Nepal!
Don’t forget — when you visit Nepal, visit Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant once! 

📍 Top floor of Hotel Nepalaya, Thamel, Kathmandu
🌐

Welcome to Nepalaya Rooftop Garden Restaurant! 

Take a break from the busy streets of Thamel and relax on our peaceful rooftop. Enjoy delicious food, warm hospitality, and stunning views of Kathmandu and the Himalayas 

From authentic Nepali Thali and momo to biryani and wood-fired pizza, every dish is fresh, flavorful, and made to delight 🍲🍕

Bring your friends, watch the sunset, and create unforgettable memories high above the city ❤️

📍 Hotel Nepalaya Rooftop, Thamel, Kathmandu
🌐

Welcome to Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant – Taste the Flavor, Feel the View! 

Escape the city noise and enjoy peaceful dining above the heart of Thamel, Kathmandu 
Savor mouth-watering dishes — from Nepali Thali, Paneer Chilli, and Biryani to Cheese Balls and Pizza — all prepared with love and served with a smile 

Enjoy the fresh air, mountain breeze, and beautiful city view — perfect for travelers, families, and friends! 

📍 Hotel Nepalaya Rooftop Restaurant, Thamel, Kathmandu
🌐

Experience the Taste of Nepal — Above the City! 
Welcome to Nepalaya Rooftop Garden Restaurant, where every meal comes with a breathtaking view of Kathmandu’s skyline and the Himalayas beyond.

 Enjoy our freshly prepared Nepalese Thali, Biryani, Pizza, Paneer Chilli, Cheese Balls, and more!
